description: This file is the entry point for a React-based frontend application. It sets up the React rendering process, imports essential libraries and components, and mounts the main App component into the DOM.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root React node attached to the DOM element with ID 'root' for rendering React components.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree starting with the <App /> component inside the created root.
